Package it.polimi.travlendarplus.RESTful.messages.tripMessages

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddDistanceTicketMessage
    This is the message class sent in the body of an HTTP request to add a distance ticket into the user's profile
    AddGenericTicketMessage
    This is the message class sent in the body of an HTTP request to add a generic ticket into the user's profile
    AddPathTicketMessage
    This is the message class sent in the body of an HTTP request to add a path ticket into the user's profile
    AddPeriodTicketMessage  
    AddPublicTravelMeanMessage
    This is an helper message class used to contain the name and the type of the travel means that can be associated to a ticket
    AddTicketMessage
    This is a generic message class sent in the body of an HTTP request to add a ticket into the user's profile, it is to be extended by all ticket messages
    PeriodTicketResponse
    This is a message class sent to reply with all needed info to a getTickets request with the infos about a period ticket
    TicketListResponse
    This is a message class sent to reply with all needed info to a getTickets request with a proper and readable response message
    TripMessage
    This is the main message class used to perform trip functionalities requests; It has to be extended by all messages used to request to such functionalities.
    TripResponse
    This is the main response message class used to reply to all related to trip functionalities requests; It has to be extended by all messages used to reply to such user requests
